    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, deseed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> roughly</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> black olives</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
